headline: Evercore ISI Group Maintains In-Line on Ingersoll Rand, Raises Price Target to $94
summary: Evercore ISI Group  analyst David Raso   maintains Ingersoll Rand (NYSE:IR) with a In-Line and raises the price target from $82 to $94.
